Then $PQ = Q'P',$ so triangle $PP'Q'$ is the reflection of triangle $PQQ'$ across the line $y = mx + b.$  Thus, $Q$ is the midpoint of $\overline{PP'}.$

Since $Q$ lies on the line $y = mx + b,$ we can write
